<h1 local-id=3D"8656f6cf9c4e" id=3D"REVIEWDRAFT:PIMSServices&amp;SolutionsO=
verviewandRoadmap-Goals"><img class=3D"emoticon emoticon-blue-star" data-em=
oji-id=3D"26bd" data-emoji-shortname=3D":soccer:" data-emoji-fallback=3D"=
=E2=9A=BD" src=3D"0b24eea119031e5ab95ac6b39e0deac1bf68001f2b3b76719f610cfb0=
1bc7ae3" width=3D"16" height=3D"16" data-emoticon-name=3D"blue-star" alt=3D=
"(blue star)"> Goals</h1>
<ul local-id=3D"64f4649a28be">
<li local-id=3D"27d8bbaeb7af">
<p local-id=3D"d0ebe1313608">Outline key <strong>Must's, Should's &amp; Cou=
ld's</strong> principles for key real-time documentation for all solutions =
&amp; services deployed within public cloud &amp; on-premise.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"90bf8f88e77d">
<p local-id=3D"8ef121e18d03">Have a priority to have a proactive approach t=
o workloads and deliverables. Especially including product and commercial.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a1e9adb478f6">
<p local-id=3D"91089dac4771">Create an automated documentation solution for=
 any Dev, Stg, and Production solutions and services we have at Optum/EMIS.=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"87e99d6e2041">
<p local-id=3D"9dd8f26a4ef2">This is an open goal at the time of writing to=
 create a near as possibe automated way of generating, updating &amp; maint=
aining documentation. This <strong>should</strong> include AI or AI Agents.=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"bd6f6965672a">
<li local-id=3D"d649fa35b34c">
<p local-id=3D"0297f93e0710">Covering any public cloud services &amp; solut=
ions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfcce8ce3a33">
<p local-id=3D"78332135c382">Covering any on-premise services &amp; solutio=
ns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2267d83d456">
<p local-id=3D"e347e813de83">Automating documentation from VMWare vSphere s=
tack</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4af221e9fe84">
<p local-id=3D"e50d9d00ba71">Automating documentation from GitHub Repo=E2=
=80=99s</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"a224340290f1">
<p local-id=3D"f5e4dd9cb355">Link any relevant =E2=80=98Goals &amp; Ways of=
 Working=E2=80=99, =E2=80=98Guides &amp; Templates=E2=80=99, =E2=80=98Refer=
ence Architecture=E2=80=99, =E2=80=98Architecture Landscape=E2=80=99 pages =
as reference content and guidelines to follow.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f75028ce7927">
<p local-id=3D"fbd2d9eb236f">Link any relevant =E2=80=98Core Infrastructure=
=E2=80=99, =E2=80=98Build Sheets=E2=80=99, =E2=80=98 Infrastructure Handove=
r=E2=80=99 pages as reference content and guidelines to follow.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca90a0562084">
<p local-id=3D"0a4c58365d20">Solution <strong>must</strong> support all tea=
ms where applicable in detailing what resources and configuration a solutio=
n or service is made up of. Particularly for MI/IIs, understanding the purp=
ose of a solution/service. Or building a detailed discovery report for a mi=
gration / refresh bases p</p></li>
</ul>
