l</span></h2>
<p local-id=3D"592fd47444c0">You will have to log a ticket with SecOps - <a=
 class=3D"external-link" data-card-appearance=3D"inline" href=3D"https://em=
ishealthgroup.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/1/group/3/create/10=
332" local-id=3D"3cbf27b1a651" rel=3D"nofollow">https://emishealthgroup.atl=
assian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/1/group/3/create/10332</a></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ed054b98fa96">
<li local-id=3D"bff65175-290b-41c9-8498-721766684bf8">
<p local-id=3D"5c66549fe32d">Create <strong>Holistic=E2=80=91Viewer</strong=
> permission set with:<br><code>ViewOnlyAccess</code> + <code>SecurityAudit=
</code> + <code>AWSResourceExplorerReadOnlyAccess</code> (+ inline Cost Exp=
lorer reads if needed). <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://docs.aws=
.amazon.com/aws-managed-policy/latest/reference/ViewOnlyAccess.html" rel=3D=
"nofollow">[docs.aws.amazon.com]</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f01cf50-b258-4b56-974e-4752e5eba07a">
<p local-id=3D"dbf8b2d1c8e3">(Optional) Attach a <strong>permissions bounda=
ry</strong> to enforce =E2=80=9Cno writes/no sensitive reads=E2=80=9D.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"160b6fd4-efa9-43e2-9196-5bc6a8b9c0a6">
<p local-id=3D"ba11a6547c10">Assign the permission set to all target accoun=
ts/OUs (users/groups).</p></li>
</ul>
