<li local-id=3D"47e6d4f2e886">
<p local-id=3D"5f2a4dbebf79">The creation of YAML templates &gt;&gt; For st=
andard and core configuration. This would include Core Infrastructure Detai=
l, Reference Architecture, VMWare detail (See Dan K for guide).</p></li>
