<p local-id=3D"fc345b5f4e3a">Creation of HCL files &gt;&gt; Contain terrafo=
rm configuration. Do these meet the current standards?</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a1549c66046b">
<p local-id=3D"8b62ad8696b9">Could Infra Architects or AI agents get read-o=
nly access to:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e4b077785ba1">
<li local-id=3D"b021731e4da7">
<p local-id=3D"80f07c19bce0">All GitHub Repo=E2=80=99s</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"71455bca21de">
<p local-id=3D"f729fe7fab47">All AWS accounts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5514882ad93c">
